      • transactionWithSuggestedFeePerByte

        @Deprecated
public static Transaction transactionWithSuggestedFeePerByte​(Transaction copyTx,
                                                             BigInteger suggestedFeePerByte)
                                                      throws NoSuchAlgorithmException
        Deprecated.
        Replaced by setFeeByFeePerByte(com.algorand.algosdk.transaction.Transaction, java.math.BigInteger). This is unsafe to use because the returned transaction is a shallow copy of copyTx.
        Creates a version of the given transaction with fee populated according to suggestedFeePerByte * estimateTxSize.
        Parameters:
        copyTx - transaction to populate fee field
        suggestedFeePerByte - suggestedFee given by network
        Returns:
        transaction with proper fee set
        Throws:
        NoSuchAlgorithmException - could not estimate tx encoded size.
